<br>
Selfish ? Hell ya I am selfish . Scare? You better beleave it . Unamerican ? Hell no . If my husband got called in for the draft , I would be scared shitless , but I would support him in going . Run off to Canada ? Not an option for me . <br>
<br>
I don't see it as unamerican to be scared of going to war . Seeing as most of the people in my generation have only seen one war , the Gulf war , and we were too young to really understand it . So we are scared . Most of us have never seen a person shot before our eyes , most of us have never felt a rifle in our hands , most of us have never shot anything , be it a can , a animal or a human being . <br>
<br>
My hat goes off to those in the armed forces that keep this nation free . I like my freedom , we all do . Alot of us can't do what they do to keep us free. Alot of us are scared to do what they do to keep us free. I or my husband , or my cousin , or her husband were drafted , we wouldnt like it ,we would be scared ,but we would go to defend our families and keep us free . <br>
<br>
Just becuase someone is scared , doesnt mean they are unamerican , or anything like that , it just means they are scared . Call me a hippie if you want to , but I hate wars . They scare me . To know that people are dieing becuase of one ( or many ) crazy person ( people) . <br>
<br>
Minah,make love not war,Trueheart<br>
